{"tid":241760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[簡單易整］ 節瓜蝦滑","createTime":"2017-05-13T11:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T17:03:49.000Z","uid":107051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14d73ffc367b9af9cd0b098cd432b856572bbaf9","tid":241760,"uid":107051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T11:39:42.000Z","msg":"聽日母親節啦，平時食母親煮嘅嘢多，試下整返樣餸慰勞下佢~  整完先打算開po 所以遲啲補圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/192428_7314b3dd406c9a332756bfdf5601eebb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F192428_7314b3dd406c9a332756bfdf5601eebb.jpg&h=2b962418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實步驟好簡單 <br />\n材料係節瓜同蝦滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用具： 一隻匙，刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想整幾多就買幾多，一條瓜大約切到五舊<br />\n刨好皮就切（注意要有一定厚度，因為要釀啲蝦滑<br />\n切完之後用隻匙將中間啲肉整出黎（唔好整穿個底）<br />\n&gt;&gt;&gt;放啲蝦滑入去<br />\n拎去蒸三十分鐘左右<br />\n完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/193838_8d7c1fc45d4d36fe5b674b36a0eb69d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F193838_8d7c1fc45d4d36fe5b674b36a0eb69d8.jpg&h=22964040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已經好盡力影靚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc9867536e7f3defdb02a451d3ab9e117068f8d","tid":241760,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T11:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bcc6a14d267fb9e5593615400bc1d8a2facd59","tid":241760,"uid":107051,"like":1,"dislike"